{{Galaxy cluster | name = NGC 2997 group of galaxies | image = [[File:NGC 2997 ESO.jpg|300px]] | type = Loose galaxy group | GC_l = 250 | GC_b = 19 | SGC_L = 133 | SGC_B = -53 | constellation = [[Hydra (constellation)|Hydra]] / [[Antlia]] | distance = [[1 E22 m|24.8 million]] | main_member = [[NGC 2997]] }}
The '''NGC 2997 group''' is a [[group of galaxies]] about [[1 E22 m|24.8 million]] [[light-year]]s from [[Earth]] containing [[NGC 2997]] as a member. It is a group in the [[Local Supercluster]] along with the [[Local Group]].
